name:                binpack2d
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            2D bin packing algorithm.
description:         Bottom left skyline algorithm feeding wastage to
                     a bestfit guillotine algorithm with a minor
                     modification, which sorts fragments by y coordinate and
                     then by x coordinate. This allows it to combine new
                     fragments with adjacent ones, if they are aligned and
                     have the same height.
